    "English": "An exclusive <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Exosuit Appearance Override</span>.<br><br>A fusion of advanced technology and resinous organic secretions, this hardened carapace represents the apex of bio-organic engineering.<br><br>Transform the appearance of your Exosuit at an <span class=\"name name-technology\">Appearance Modifier</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "专属的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">套装外观</span>。<br><br>通过融合先进技术与类似树脂的有机分泌物，这种硬化甲壳代表着生物有机工程学的顶点。<br><br>可以在<span class=\"name name-technology\">外观修改器</span>使用以更改你的套装外观。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "獨特的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">強化套裝外觀覆寫</span>。<br><br>這款硬化外殼結合先進科技與有機樹脂分泌物，展現生物有機工程的極致成就。<br><br>在<span class=\"name name-technology\">外觀改造器</span>改變你的強化套裝外觀。"
